(12, 1, '2014-04-08 08:40:40', '2014-04-08 08:40:40', 'This is an example page. It''s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I''m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin'' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href="http://oracle.mointernational-clients.co.uk/wp-admin/">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!', 'Sample Page', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-04-08 08:40:40', '2014-04-08 08:40:40', '', 2, 'http://oracle.mointernational-clients.co.uk/?p=12', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(13, 1, '2014-04-08 08:41:01', '2014-04-08 08:41:01', '<h1>Service Innovation</h1>\r\n<div class="col-md-6">\r\n\r\nFaced with technologically-savvy consumers and agile new competitors, financial services organizations are increasingly looking to design and deliver innovative new services. But in a fast-changing environment, how can you identify and prioritize the innovations that will meet the organization’s strategic objectives and deliver the best returns?\r\n\r\nAn Enterprise Project Portfolio Management (EPPM) solution can help your organization balance technological innovation with the need to maintain and develop existing, business-critical systems. With a clearer view of all assets across the enterprise, IT and business functions can improve project selection, execution, and success—while optimizing resources to support continued innovation.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-6">\r\n\r\nOracle’s EnterpriseTrack is a leading, cloud-based PPM solution that can help you to:\r\n<ul class="list-unstyled custom-list">\r\n	<li>Prioritize the most promising development projects</li>\r\n	<li>Optimize work and resource management</li>\r\n	<li>Facilitate continuous improvement</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nExplore the resources below to discover how EPPM is enabling financial institutions to deliver true service innovation.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Service Innovation', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'service-innovation', '', '', '2014-04-23 09:21:20', '2014-04-23 09:21:20', '', 0, 'http://oracle.mointernational-clients.co.uk/?page_id=13', 0, 'page', '', 0),
