(19, 1, '2014-04-08 08:58:46', '2014-04-08 08:58:46', 'Banking executives maintain a cautious optimism for the near-term business outlook, expecting modest improvements in revenue, the economy, and hiring in 2013 but remain guarded longer term, not seeing a complete economic recovery until 2014. Learn how a Project Portfolio Management solution for financial services can manage uncertainty by:\r\n\r\n<ul class="list-unstyled custom-list">\r\n<li>Providing transparency</li>\r\n<li>Aligning your business strategy</li>\r\n<li>Monitoring execution and regulatory compliance</li>\r\n<li>Balancing risk and opportunities</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'Managing Macroeconomic Uncertainty in a Post-Recession World', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '9-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-04-08 08:58:46', '2014-04-08 08:58:46', '', 9, 'http://oracle.mointernational-clients.co.uk/uncategorized/9-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
